	<h1 class="title">5个年轻设计师为索尼推出了概念款，作品办了个展</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/112316/small/112316.JPG?1442220004" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">罗芊 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-05-22 08:20:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/9807/medium/9807.jpg?1436655038" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


